lead_paragraph: Peter Holland scored the go-ahead goal early in the third period, Jonathan Bernier stopped 39 shots, and the Toronto Maple Leafs beat the St. Louis Blues 4-1 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Holland Scores Go-Ahead Goal, Maple Leafs Beat Blues 4-1
